          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-2.webp" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Ayesha</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Developer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8"> “As a busy professional, I don’t have time to read through countless articles. This app saves me so much time by delivering news podcasts that are relevant to my interests. Highly recommend it!”</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
