        </div>
        <p class="mt-8"> “The quality of the AI-generated audio is impressive. It feels like listening to a professional news broadcast. Plus, the ability to customize my news feed is a game-changer.”</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
